column1: Daily Weather Observations for Hobart, Tasmania for January 2013
Prepared at 16:09 UTC on Wednesday  7 August 2013   IDCJDW7021.201301
Most observations from Battery Point, but some from Hobart Airport.
On average, there is slightly more sunshine at the airport than in the city.
Temperature, humidity, wind, pressure, cloud and rainfall observations are from Hobart (Ellerslie Road) {station 094029}
Evaporation and sunshine observations are from Hobart Airport {station 094008}
